Hot 7’s is a 5-coin classic slot-game that has three reels and one payline! &lt;br/&gt; Actually high payouts are provided for combinations of Seven symbols. The game involves a Jackpot feature, thus, 2% of each bet placed in the game goes to the common pot. You will hit a Jackpot with three Triple Seven symbols lined up, note, that to qualify for winning a Jackpot you need to have 5-coin bet placed.